{"tid":1737590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麥康奈爾：香港示威者是「勇敢的男女」 特朗普要為香港示威者發聲","createTime":"2019-11-19T04:00:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T04:53:22.000Z","uid":184679,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0d4000751540dbe307aa4499737e4bd0313607ad","tid":1737590,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:00:37.000Z","msg":"香港示威愈演烈、美國參議院審議《香港人權與民主法案》之際，美國總統特朗普至今仍未有表態。參議院多數派（共和黨）領袖麥康奈爾（Mitch McConnell）敦促，特朗普為香港示威者發聲，指「世界應從特朗普口中直接聽到」美國支持香港示威者。麥康奈爾又形容，香港示威者是「勇敢的男女」（brave women and men）。<br />\n<br />\n麥康奈爾稱，特朗普不應只將貿易，而應該同時將香港自治情況，作為美國與中國雙邊接觸的議題。美國參議院正審議《香港人權與民主法案》，法案規定華府定期審視香港自治狀況，是否仍然符合美國將香港視為獨立關稅區的條件，並要求華府制裁「侵犯香港人權」責任方。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2500695</code></pre>"},{"pid":"d7f0fe81a3698b0abfd838816eeb605ebb112c2a","tid":1737590,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:50:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"604acc3d153332665846ff7f261aad55102cc129","tid":1737590,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:53:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}